snippet.textDisplay:
Complicated. Serbia has a 13 times higher death rate from Covid 19 than Australia per capita (13.5k deaths v 2.5, 10 million pop v 25 million).
We have strong institutions, economy and take Covid very seriously.
We are egalitarian, meaning no special treatment for stars versus a worker; this is why the majority of Australians (70%) support deportation for Novax.  
It didn't help Novax that 1. He or his team falsely filled in an immigration form saying he hadn't travelled internationally two weeks prior and 2. He was not isolating when he received a positive Covid result on Dec 16.
This was a very bad look that outraged the Australian public.

Australians honor rules and laws (we have compulsory voting too!)

Big picture, the Vax saves the individual, family and society members, its selfish to not take it if you can take it. Freedom comes with Responsibly. All freedom and no responsibility - civil society  dies.
